node.text:
EPIC video from Finns Beach Club! They’ve partnered with Bali Tourism Board, Wonderful Indonesia and Garuda Airlines with an incredible offer to get the world #backtobali ! 
When you buy a Back To Bali voucher, your initial payment TRIPLES in value to spend on food and drinks, accommodation and Finns Bali memberships during your next holiday to Bali, plus exclusive access to discounts on accommodation, adventures, dining experiences and more! 
Here’s the link for vouchers - these are 100% going to sell out so get in quick. https://finns.to/SagQ3
I’ve got mine - I’ll see you in Bali! 
Follow @finnsbeachclub for more info.

node.text:
Pressure 
The strongest souls of this world are those that have both felt immense pressure, and overcome it 
This Lion King didn’t get here by cowering away from opposition; even when it’s 20 to 1 
And even with help, that is why he is the King 
Video by © BBC Earth @bbcearth

node.text:
Hippos have the ability to lock their jaws at nearly 180 degree angles 😍 This feature, which makes a hippo look like it's yawning, is particularly important when hippos end up in conflict with other animals. The wide opening angle means that hippos can produce a bite force of 1,800 PSI—enough to break bones and snap wooden planks in two.

📽 @cincinnatizoo
